## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **afami-cel afamitresgene autoleucel Tecelra 2024** = first FDA TCR-T — synovial sarcoma + MAGE-A4 + HLA-A*02:01-restricted. CAR-T 와 distinct: HLA presentation 의존 + intracellular antigen 인식. quantum-VQE 의 peptide-MHC-TCR triad scaffold 가 직접 fit. small-molecule mimetic 가 next paradigm.
2. **tazemetostat Tazverik 2020** = first FDA EZH2 inhibitor — INI1(SMARCB1)-deficient epithelioid sarcoma + 만성 follicular lymphoma (cross-lymphoma). PRC2 epigenetic 표적 first-in-class. quantum-VQE 의 SAM-pocket leverage.
3. **nirogacestat Ogsiveo 2023** = first FDA gamma-secretase inhibitor — adult desmoid tumor (CTNNB1 + APC β-catenin pathway). Notch signaling proxy disease modification. quantum-VQE 의 transmembrane intramembrane protease pocket 한정.
4. **larotrectinib + entrectinib NTRK 2018-2019** = tissue-agnostic — sarcoma + 다른 solid tumor 통합. fusion-driven sarcoma 의 paradigm. quantum-VQE 의 fusion-kinase ATP-pocket 단순.
5. **pexidartinib + vimseltinib CSF-1R 2019-2025** = TGCT (tenosynovial giant cell tumor) — benign-like locally-aggressive disease 적응증 신설. CSF-1R PPI scaffold.
6. **trabectedin + lurbinectedin marine-derived 2015-2020** = DNA minor-groove + RNA Pol II — natural product-derived novel mechanism. 만성 LPS + LMS + SCLC cross-disease.
7. **doxorubicin + ifosfamide 35+ year 1L STS** = cytotoxic chemo 가 1L 표준 — 50+ subtype heterogeneous + targeted 가 subtype-specific only. 임상 paradigm 의 conservative.
8. **PD-1 sarcoma 한정** = pembro/nivo single-agent 전체 STS 효과 modest — UPS + DDLPS subtype 한정 evidence. SARC028 + alliance trial subset analysis.
9. **selumetinib Koselugo 2020 NF1** = first FDA plexiform neurofibroma — 소아 + 만성 inherited. MEK1/2 RAS pathway. (cross-pediatric_rare + inherited_adult)
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, sarcoma 50+ subtype 임상 의미 한정. K-sarcoma framework 산정특례 + 식약처 별도 review 필요.

